 The dark warrior woke up from his slumber. His gears creaked. He had been 
stuck in stasis lock for a long time. This hero of old had a long journey 
ahead of him. Hopefully the maximals had survived. His sensors picked up a 
large structure. He saw a visual on his arm. It was a maximal city. How 
beautiful it was. he transformed into his vehichle mode and drove off to the 
site.

--part1_83.e53ecbd.28a5fa56_boundary
